node.title: Vehicle crashes through overbridge, dropping to motorway below
node.description: There are delays on State Highway 1's southbound lanes in Auckland this morning after a vehicle crashed through the overbridge last night, falling onto the motorway below.
node.content:
["There are delays on State Highway 1's southbound lanes in Auckland this morning after a vehicle crashed through the overbridge last night, falling onto the motorway below.", "", "
The vehicle crashed through the overbridge barriers just before 4am, dropping to the motorway below Photo: WAKA KOTAHI
", "The vehicle was travelling along Hill Rd, Manurewa, about 3.37am when it lost control, crashing through the barriers and dropped onto the motorway below, police said in a statement.", "The sole occupant became trapped and had to be cut free by emergency services.", "The injured person's condition was described as life-threatening.", "The motorway between Hill Rd and Takanini was closed this morning, but the left lane has since reopened. Motorists are warned to expect delays as contractors continue to clear the area."]
